snippet.title: Thomas Foster musicproduction
snippet.description:
This is my YouTube Channel Thomas Foster music production.
Here you find Tutorials for the most important DAWs like Ableton, Logic Pro, Bitwig and FL Studio and the most important Plugins like Omnisphere, Nexus 3, Kontakt and more. Thank you for joining my channel, have fun and enjoy 😊
